{"tid":1789841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信 HSBC 強烈要求公開交代","createTime":"2019-12-19T14:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T13:41:43.000Z","uid":307356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bec023794617793aecfe67d25affd23ccad1840","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">齊齊 send email 去 hk_mediarelations@hsbc.com.hk，要求 HSBC 交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">可參考：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Subject: </strong><br />\nSpark Alliance HK's HK$70M got frozen by the HK police<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Body:</strong><br />\nDear HSBC media team,<br />\n<br />\nI am writing to express my serious concern on the operations transparency and integrity of HSBC with regards to the most recent incident in which a fund valued HK$70M of the Spark Alliance HK got frozen by the Hong Kong Police Force today. <br />\n<br />\nPlease immediately respond to the public on below questions in order to eliminate all the doubts that the public has.<br />\n- Has the Spark Alliance bank account already been closed in HSBC before this incident happened?<br />\n- What kind of information related to the Spark Alliance bank account has HSBC passed to the Hong Kong Police Force?<br />\n- What is the current status of the fund?<br />\n<br />\nHSBC is one of the famous banks with high reputation in Hong Kong. Many Hong Kong citizens own at least an account in HSBC. I am afraid that HSBC can no longer be trusted if all the doubts cannot be resolved.<br />\n<br />\nRegards,<br />\nHong Kong citizen</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>利申：本人英文能力有限</strong>"},{"pid":"c16dc04afa0e63aa0f96afb74d62a45ef0806d01","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:40:19.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"d61151cd879b5709490916d09266f06dc2ca6f15","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"502de802ec088a6e0a16e13d4e3ea5cbaadb92aa","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"c686e53b0844c624202d049eae7ef2568cf3b499","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:40:51.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"bf08fbabad193d6624365cf6c00cf9c261acb610","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"8a532e7e8b5f07b37b14925cfb58243603fda35f","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"7e00ca6ae174c48e64148dc001ab42e340dfc8ff","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"e24a29b565be66742033f8ed7eb5cc2d9f26d708","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"推8"},{"pid":"0cb21671a82dc2762828c11833d65f0669bcee56","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"推9"},{"pid":"2f7d7ae1de1835dff2abe986e4498ae9e06a5f27","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"f6b1b5352d16f8babbf5ff054cedc9d0912ca1ed","tid":1789841,"uid":307356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19